data.description: 3bed 2 bath, Beautiful updated brick & vinyl home situated on private 1.3 acre lot. From the moment you pull up the professional landscape of Hydrangeas & Blueberry Garden draws you right in. Irrigation to Hydrangea area, blueberries, and front porch. Covered front porch perfect for morning coffee. Interior features: Bamboo flooring through main level living areas. Living room gas brick fireplace for those cold Winter nights. Large freshly updated kitchen with bar seating and dining area with huge double pantries, new countertops. Kitchen, dining room, living room and hallway freshly painted. The newer back deck, perfect for grilling and family time looks over a private fenced backyard that also has workshop with power. Hall bath updated and added laundry area. Spacious primary bedroom updated bath with double vanity vessel sinks and gas heater. Wide open, walk out basement with windows on three side with 2nd laundry area would make perfect in- law-suite, teenage game room or man cave.
